<item>
            <title>[CXF-4953] JAXRSClientFactoryBean doesn&apos;t take the bus features into consideration </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-4953</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we set the feature into to bus, the feature should be applied to all the JAXRSClientFactoryBean by default.&lt;br/&gt;
Current JAXRSClientFactoryBean just take the features which are set to itself into consideration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12641377">CXF-4953</key>
            <summary>JAXRSClientFactoryBean doesn&apos;t take the bus features into consideration </summary>
